{"tid":1275921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持警察！！","createTime":"2019-07-02T00:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T02:39:12.000Z","uid":24265,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ebf347fd6f932e47188590e6c786a5fdae4671f","tid":1275921,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"咪撚屌住先 岩岩見到個post好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n【鐵証】癲狗開無雙 打退後緊嘅示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275077</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry 唔識post gif<br />\n<br />\n係個gif度見到佢地得一隻狗係咁打<br />\n支那咁撚鐘意分化 我地係咪應該要分化佢地先呢 老實講 無可否認係有一少少少部份正常警察<br />\n我估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有一少部份係支持我地 但香港呢個地方份工 份糧真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣係咪可以由呢方面著手 由班狗內部分化先 橫掂佢地都咁撚鐘意割席<br />\n<br />\n佢地自己一哥帶頭割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等佢地大家知道一啲無打淨係趕 同另一班無雙狗 速龍係唔同<br />\nSorry 講到1999 <br />\n實質應該點做 番返比各大巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外起底要起撚埋佢地d屋企人 朋友 女朋友 千祈唔好玩人地電話同叫外賣<br />\n<br />\n等無人想同d狗做朋友 另一半<br />\n有人唔做 做狗係有後果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 班含家產咁樣打 真係要推到佢坐監"},{"pid":"58e173b06ffe1bbbfbe28e5f6b607fe8461c7f28","tid":1275921,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:22:59.000Z","msg":"一早試下10連"},{"pid":"549bd9e7a09d6ef21a46803a740b3835a8f72ede","tid":1275921,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:23:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"22d908061bc29cea35c4aa8fb7fec32ee732a980","tid":1275921,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:23:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5970c82a177a8e822ec47a1bd1e9585c09aaf793","tid":1275921,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,